The two fields are configured to automagically get updated when tiddlers are renamed. Using the excellent relink plugin (see https://github.com/flibbles/tw5-relink).

The relink configuration is provided by these two tiddlers: 

* $:/config/flibbles/relink/fields/tiddler_sequencer_list
* $:/config/flibbles/relink/fields/tiddler_sequencer_parent
